    "text": "Crown rust resistance is described in oat diploid species A. strigosa accession PI 258731. Resistance from PI 258731 is introgressed into hexaploid A. sativa germplasm. This study maps QTL for resistance in PI 258731. It evaluates the number of QTL. It understands the relationship between the genomic location in A. strigosa and the introgression location in A. sativa. It identifies molecular markers linked with PI 258731 resistance loci. These markers could be used for marker assisted selection and detection of this resistance in diverse A. strigosa accessions.",
